OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777903634
OL,3,CTen people released on bail following
OL,4,Craids on religious group
OL,6,FTen people arrested in connection with
OL,7,Fallegations of serious sexual
OL,8,Foffences, forced marriage, and modern
OL,9,Fslavery within a religious group have
OL,10,Fbeen released on conditional bail.
OL,12,FSeven men and three women were
OL,13,Farrested following a large-scale
OL,14,Foperation by Cheshire Police in Crewe.
OL,16,FThe investigation follows reports of
OL,17,Foffences allegedly committed in 2023
OL,18,Fagainst a woman while she was a member
OL,19,Fof the religious group, Ahmadi
OL,20,FReligion of Peace and Light.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
