FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777903634
OL,3,CTen people released on bail following
OL,4,Craids on religious group
OL,6,FMore than 500 officers executed
OL,7,Fwarrants at three separate addresses
OL,8,Fin the town on Wednesday, 29 April,
OL,9,Fincluding the group's main
OL,10,Fheadquarters at Webb House, a former
OL,11,Forphanage, on Victoria Avenue.
OL,13,FIn an update on Friday, 1 May,
OL,14,FCheshire Police said all 10 suspects -
OL,15,Fof American, Mexican, Italian,
OL,16,FSpanish, Swedish and Egyptian
OL,17,Fnationalities ` have now been released
OL,18,Fon conditional bail pending further
OL,19,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777903634
OL,3,CTen people released on bail following
OL,4,Craids on religious group
OL,6,FOfficers have applied for Slavery and
OL,7,FTrafficking Risk Orders (STROs)
OL,8,Fagainst five of the suspects, which
OL,9,Fprovide restrictions to individuals
OL,10,Fand "ensure there is no risk to the
OL,11,Fpublic and other members of the group."
OL,13,FThe applications for these orders are
OL,14,Fscheduled to be heard at Magistrates'
OL,15,FCourt on Friday, 1 May.
OL,17,FChief Superintendent Gareth Wrigley
OL,18,Fhas reiterated that the police's focus
OL,19,Fis on the alleged criminal activity
OL,20,Frather than the faith of the community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777903634
OL,3,CTen people released on bail following
OL,4,Craids on religious group
OL,6,F"I would also like to reiterate that
OL,7,Fis not an investigation into the
OL,8,Freligion; our investigation solely
OL,9,Ffocuses on the serious allegations
OL,10,Fwhich have been reported to us," Chief
OL,11,FSuperintendent Wrigley said.
OL,13,FHe also thanked residents for their
OL,14,Fpatience during the "disruption"
OL,15,Fcaused by the high-profile warrants
OL,16,Fand confirmed that police are working
OL,17,Fwith partners to provide safeguarding
OL,18,Fand advice to other members of the
OL,19,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777903634
OL,3,CTen people released on bail following
OL,4,Craids on religious group
OL,6,FAdditional patrols will remain in the
OL,7,Flocal area to provide reassurance to
OL,8,Fthe public, the force added.
OL,10,FChief Superintendent Wrigley said:
OL,11,F"I'd also remind residents that this
OL,12,Fremains a live investigation which
OL,13,Fwill take some time, and I would ask
OL,14,Fthat people do not speculate while the
OL,15,Fcase remains ongoing."
OL,17,FAnyone with concerns is encouraged to
OL,18,Fspeak directly with officers on patrol.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
