PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777903634
OL,3,CTen people released on bail following
OL,4,Craids on religious group
OL,6,FHe added: "I'd also remind residents
OL,7,Fthat this remains a live investigation
OL,8,Fwhich will take some time, and I would
OL,9,Fask that people do not speculate while
OL,10,Fthe case remains ongoing."
OL,12,F25 people were charged with public
OL,13,Forder offences alleged to have taken
OL,14,Fplace while the warrants were being
OL,15,Fcarried out, police said. They are due
OL,16,Fto appear before magistrates next
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,19,FAbout 150 people are believed to have
OL,20,Fbeen living at the religious
OL,21,Fcommunity's base.
